    h2 Button Styles
    p Links and buttons can be styled using the <code>button</code>, <code>button-primary</code>, <code>button-green</code>, <code>button-yellow</code> etc. classes as shown below. The default button style is same as dark button style and primary button style is same as blue button.
    .code-example
      .code-output
        div
          a.button.mr-small(href='#') Default Button
          a.button.button-primary.mr-small(href='#') Primary Button
          a.button.button-light.mr-small(href='#') Light Button
          a.button.button-gray-light.mr-small(href='#') Gray Light
          a.button.button-gray.mr-small(href='#') Gray button
          a.button.button-gray-dark.mr-small(href='#') Gray Dark
          a.button.button-dark.mr-small(href='#') Dark Button
        div
          a.button.button-blue.mr-small(href='#') Blue Button
          a.button.button-green.mr-small(href='#') Green Button
          a.button.button-yellow.mr-small(href='#') Yellow Button
          a.button.button-red.mr-small(href='#') Red Button
          a.button.button-pink.mr-small(href='#') Pink Button
          a.button.button-purple.mr-small(href='#') Purple Button
          a.button.button-teal.mr-small(href='#') Teal Button
          a.button.button-cyan.mr-small(href='#') Cyan Button
      pre
        code.
          #{'<a class="button" href="#">Default Button</a>'}
          #{'<a class="button button-primary" href="#">Primary Button</a>'}
          #{'<a class="button button-light" href="#">Light Button</a>'}
          #{'<button class="button button-ghost">Ghost Button</button>'}
          #{'<button class="button button-ghost-light">Ghost Light</button>'}
          #{'<input class="button button button-text" value="Text Button"  type="submit"/>'}

    h2 Outline Buttons
    p To make any button outline button, add <code>bg-transparent</code> and an appropriate text color using <code>text-*</code> classes as shown below.
    .code-example
      .code-output
        div
          a.button.bg-transparent.text-dark.mr-small(href='#') Default Button
          a.button.button-primary.bg-transparent.text-primary.mr-small(href='#') Primary Button
          a.button.button-light.bg-transparent.text-dark.mr-small(href='#') Light Button
          a.button.button-gray-light.bg-transparent.text-dark.mr-small(href='#') Gray Light
          a.button.button-gray.bg-transparent.text-dark.mr-small(href='#') Gray button
          a.button.button-gray-dark.bg-transparent.text-dark.mr-small(href='#') Gray Dark
          a.button.button-dark.bg-transparent.text-dark.mr-small(href='#') Dark Button
