    h2 Rounded Buttons
    p Add <code>border-rounded</code> class to make any button a rounded button.
    .code-example
      .code-output
        // Default Button Rounded
        a.button.border-rounded.mr-small(href='#') Rounded Button
        // Primary Button Rounded
        button.button.border-rounded.button-primary.mr-small Rounded Primary
        // Light Button Rounded
        button.button.border-rounded.button-light.mr-small Rounded Light
        // Ghost Button Rounded
        button.button.button-ghost.border-rounded.mr-small Rounded Ghost
        // Ghost Light Rounded
        button.button.button-ghost-light.border-rounded.mr-small Rounded Ghost Light
